Package: SDMDashboardWorkbench
Type: Shiny
Title: Local Species Distribution Modelling Dashboard Workbench
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("SDM Dashboard Workbench contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: A local R/Shiny workbench for species distribution modelling from presence-only observation records with WorldClim climate layers, optional OpenTopography elevation, optional HWSD v2 soil covariates, spatial thinning, and spatial-block cross-validation diagnostics.
